reviews.review_text: Whole show is on point Great energy, the whole band is hot and JG rides the wave. China > Rider, Estimated, are highlights. The entire show is worth a listen.
Great Show! Following a great show the day before.  Nothing like dancing in the dirt at the fairgrounds!
